">https://calvinrosser.com/why-relationships-fail/  </a>
<br>4. When you want them to change according to you
<br>5. If you are angry or fighting, still choose to sleep rather than resolving issues
<br>6. When your opinion seems to be more important than the right thing
<br>7. When you start becoming the so-called Relationship goals for the world.
<br>8. If you can't apologize for your mistakes, it isn't loved. Step back
<br>9. If you feel, forever is a myth
<br>10. A relationship is not a struggle for control, domination, or power; it is a struggle for making your bond
</p>

